cs213.photoAlbum.control
Class Control

java.lang.Object
  cs213.photoAlbum.control.Control
All Implemented Interfaces:
ControlInterface
public class Control
extends java.lang.Object
implements ControlInterface

This class implements the algorithmic logic of the program, decision making and data manipulation processes. It communicates with Model through BackendInterface to retrieve a specific user and manipulate it as needed. It respects the MVC architecture by the use of interfaces.

Author:
Roberto Ronderos Botero (First 12 Methods), Catalina Laverde Duarte (Last 9 Methods)
